  "rationale": "<p>Choice C is correct. Solve by substitution. From the second equation, y = 3x - 9. Substituting into the first: x + 2(3x - 9) = 10, so 7x - 18 = 10, giving x = 4. Then y = 12 - 9 = 3. So x + y = 4 + 3 = 7.</p>",
